query:
UPDATE 
                v2_job_queue 
            SET 
                scheduled_for = now() 
            FROM 
                v2_job 
            WHERE 
                v2_job_queue.id = v2_job.id AND 
                v2_job_queue.running is FALSE AND
                v2_job_queue.scheduled_for = $1 AND
                v2_job_queue.workspace_id = $2 AND
                v2_job.trigger_kind = $3 AND
                v2_job.trigger = $4
